{"tid":2016782,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[求討論] 九月立法會選戰後","createTime":"2020-05-14T15:56:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-14T16:10:59.000Z","uid":16086,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"46e309a6cdc9cf8073e5d5b588d28eae01eb2a67","tid":2016782,"uid":16086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T15:56:03.000Z","msg":"暫當選立法會已經係大多數意願，<br />\n但係必需現實咁睇，如果真俾35+，<br />\n中共政府必然DQ，甚至冇35+都DC，<br />\n甚至連入閘都入唔到。<br />\n<br />\n到時候，大家能唔能夠放低所有對舊制嘅願景，<br />\n起黎真革命。<br />\n<br />\n我知所謂「全民勇武」係好撚抽象，<br />\n同埋最後都未必成功，<br />\n但係大家可唔可以答應立會戰線失敗之後，<br />\n大家可以放低包袱勇一次？<br />\n如果可以就由今日開始習武啦好冇？<br />\n<br />\n最後戴翻個頭盔，不反對立會選戰，<br />\n但始終覺得會比中共DQ所以不能成事。"},{"pid":"47e71c15125b7398311f0aa22cede3eeae8b1538","tid":2016782,"uid":16086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T15:59:50.000Z","msg":"毒撚自推1"},{"pid":"4955070c819044dd4aeeccedd420cd102b3d808e","tid":2016782,"uid":16086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T16:00:06.000Z","msg":"毒撚自推2"},{"pid":"c7622c5ce9f0282f524abde3f02104f5faa877ed","tid":2016782,"uid":16086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T16:00:16.000Z","msg":"毒撚自推3"},{"pid":"60ddf3fd2ae3e867ac42dd90def7e53400eeda33","tid":2016782,"uid":16086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T16:00:29.000Z","msg":"收工"},{"pid":"95ba43a53b21f67c853c8c632b91cc48880b9465","tid":2016782,"uid":163937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T16:01:34.000Z","msg":"仲要睇撚住班票務主任變晒退休狗<br />\n隨時投咗等於無投"},{"pid":"3d7f3afc7d028e71ef212fc3c701095c2eb4fddc","tid":2016782,"uid":16086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"95ba43a53b21f67c853c8c632b91cc48880b9465","tid":2016782,"uid":163937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T16:01:34.000Z","msg":"仲要睇撚住班票務主任變晒退休狗<br />\n隨時投咗等於無投"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T16:03:56.000Z","msg":"換票箱絕對有可能，<br />\n問題係，<br />\n如果都去到依個地步，<br />\n仲同我講食黃店抗